<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="28Jun1921"><font color="red">ca. 28 June 1921</font>, <cite>Selected Letters</cite> (JJ to Frank Budgen): <cite>Ithaca</cite> is giving me fearful trouble. Corrected the first batch of proofs today up to Stephen on the strand which I read out to you on a memorable night in Zurich &hellip; I&apos;ll break the back of <cite>Ithaca</cite> tomorrow so &apos;elp me fucking Chroist. </div>
